snippet.title: Society for the Environment
snippet.description:
The Society for the Environment is the body responsible for the registration of environmental professionals.  We are the custodian of the Chartered Environmentalist (CEnv), Registered Environmental Practitioner (REnvP) and Registered Environmental Technician (REnvTech) registers, and since 2004 have established a sound platform as the body tasked with championing and registering the expertise of environmental professionals.

Being a CEnv, REnvP or REnvTech is about having the professional knowledge, experience and commitment to apply sustainable thinking throughout your daily working life. Having a professional registration allows you to showcase your expertise to clients, employers and peers. 

On our YouTube channel, we will be posting webinar recordings, clips from events and insight from CEnv, REnvP and REnvTech professionals. We hope you enjoy! 

Please contact us to find out more about what we do and our professional registers.
